coverage/
.shellspec-local

# mdBook build output
docs/book/
book/

# Tag-sourced releases (ADR 0010): the version lives in the git tag and the
# changelog in the GitHub Releases — never commit these. Guard against accidents.
/VERSION
/CHANGELOG.md
/CHANGELOG
